---
// src/components/About.astro
---
<section id="about" class="py-20 md:py-32 px-4 bg-[#F6F6F4]">
    <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto flex flex-col gap-16">

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="md:col-span-1">
                <h2 class="text-4xl font-medium">Hello.</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-2">
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                    I'm Akhdan, a UI designer from Indonesia. I spent the last 5 years crafting designs in the digital product space. After taking a year off to focus on personal projects, I'm now looking for something exciting to work on.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="md:col-span-1">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-gray-500">How I Can Help</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-2">
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                    I help teams identify business opportunities and collaborate with stakeholders to develop effective solutions. From user research and design strategy to UI/UX design and testing, I streamline projects to deliver products to market efficiently across both web and mobile apps.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>